Scottish Clergyman, Writer, and Historian (1780 – 1847)

For the other individuals who happened to share the name Thomas Chalmers, one might consult the [Thomas Chalmers (disambiguation)](/Thomas_Chalmers_(disambiguation)) page. It’s a veritable roll call of people who, presumably, achieved less than their namesake.

